The paper deals with fundamental graph parameters and algorithms for computing them, which suggests that it belongs to the Data Structures and Algorithms (cs.DS) category. The use of all-pairs shortest paths and the focus on graph properties also suggest Computational Geometry (cs.CG) and Discrete Mathematics (cs.DM) as likely categories. The mention of approximation algorithms and fixed parameter subquadratic algorithms suggests Numerical Analysis (cs.NA) and Complexity Theory (cs.CC) as possible categories as well.
